short_description_localized.en: Immerse yourself in Midtown. These 200-square-foot rooms offer a queen bed, and every guest enjoys daily continental breakfast.

description_localized.en: These elegant accommodations will host you in comfort without breaking the bank, so you can spend on the sights, restaurants, shows, and museums that New York is known for. Book this 200-square-foot room with a queen bed, and enjoy our proximity to the Empire State Building and much more. Max. 2 guests.
